2
00:01:30.110 --> 00:01:35.330
Future Island, Egghead

3
00:01:37.540 --> 00:01:42.420
Now that I'm aboard this ship,
I guess it's my problem, too!

4
00:01:42.420 --> 00:01:45.750
My new captain is quite the handful!

5
00:01:47.170 --> 00:01:48.250
Luffy!

6
00:01:48.670 --> 00:01:51.510
I love it! I love your dream!

7
00:01:51.510 --> 00:01:52.590
Yeah?

8
00:01:52.590 --> 00:01:54.470
It's the best!

9
00:01:55.220 --> 00:01:56.140
Whoa-whoa!

10
00:01:56.140 --> 00:01:58.560
Yeah, that's just like you...

11
00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:03.190
But you gotta be the Pirate King
to make it happen!

12
00:02:03.190 --> 00:02:08.320
We're just one lode poneglyph away
from setting course for Laugh Tale!

13
00:02:08.320 --> 00:02:10.990
Don't make it sound so simple, Franky.

14
00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:16.530
That last lode poneglyph will be
the most difficult one to find.

15
00:02:19.290 --> 00:02:20.660
Because...

16
00:02:21.080 --> 00:02:23.290
unlike the others,

17
00:02:24.040 --> 00:02:28.670
no one has found it for a very long time...

18
00:02:29.050 --> 00:02:31.300
There are no leads whatsoever.

19
00:02:40.970 --> 00:02:42.810
Marine Headquarters
New World

20
00:02:45.060 --> 00:02:48.150
Signal from Flame Emperor Sabo
to the Kamabakka Queendom!

21
00:02:48.150 --> 00:02:48.900
Alright!

22
00:02:48.900 --> 00:02:50.650
Where is he?!

23
00:02:50.650 --> 00:02:52.400
Make sure you trace his position!

24
00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:54.860
No jamming from a white transponder snail!

25
00:02:54.860 --> 00:02:58.240
He's done nothing to prevent wiretapping?

26
00:02:58.240 --> 00:03:01.200
This must be an emergency call!
It won't last long!

27
00:03:01.200 --> 00:03:03.910
We finally got a lead on his whereabouts!

28
00:03:04.290 --> 00:03:06.040
Don't miss this chance!

29
00:03:06.540 --> 00:03:10.250
Room of Authority
Pangaea Castle
The Holy Land, Mary Geoise

30
00:03:14.720 --> 00:03:16.680
The trace was successful!

31
00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:17.800
Where is it from?!

32
00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:20.810
The Kingdom of Lulusia!

33
00:03:22.060 --> 00:03:23.640
Lulusia...

34
00:03:23.640 --> 00:03:24.890
My word...

35
00:03:24.890 --> 00:03:29.440
It's one of the countries where
the simultaneous Eight-Nation Revolution

36
00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:31.980
took place after the Reverie!

37
00:03:31.980 --> 00:03:34.820
It's an ideal hiding spot for Sabo!

38
00:03:35.450 --> 00:03:37.160
I see...

39
00:03:37.160 --> 00:03:39.120
What an unfortunate man...

40
00:03:40.740 --> 00:03:42.330
No...

41
00:03:44.120 --> 00:03:46.160
This is simply fate...

42
00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:51.590
Kamabakka Queendom

43
00:03:51.590 --> 00:03:53.710
Great! I got through!

44
00:03:56.220 --> 00:03:57.430
Sabo...

45
00:03:57.430 --> 00:03:58.800
Sabo!

46
00:03:58.800 --> 00:04:01.930
We haven't heard from you
in a while, so what gives?!

47
00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:06.140
I vass really voorried about you!

48
00:04:06.140 --> 00:04:07.770
I'm sorry, everyone.

49
00:04:07.770 --> 00:04:09.310
No!

50
00:04:09.310 --> 00:04:10.520
That's okay!

51
00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:12.020
We love you!

52
00:04:12.020 --> 00:04:14.780
That's enough celebrating.

53
00:04:14.780 --> 00:04:19.530
You didn't contact us just to
tell us you're alive, did you?

54
00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:22.370
No...

55
00:04:22.370 --> 00:04:26.250
I suppose you've all read
the news article by now.

